flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("", "036AB25A41AA3923544FA4A69717628E", "Outside the walls of Aela, I met a beggar at night. He was an outcast searching for kindness, something not afforded to him by the locals. I offered him coin, and in return he gave me all that he had, a rusty key bearing the image of a Cloak and Gavel.")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("", "059B30184FE3D879CB1AB298AA44ADA4", "Find the chest that the Cloak and Gavel key opens.")
calloutDescription: NSLOCTEXT("[D20C99C24B2FABB4DC05E3BF1EE067C5]", "DF2A17A8407DD716685D2B8E243A19EE", "A man sits in the dirt with his arms outstretched and palms cupped. His cheeks are hollow and his bones are visible under his skin.")
